OL,9,     Gthreats to his leadership and
OL,10,     Gensure an heir.
OL,11,G0055FDynasties II
OL,12,     GIn the wild Patagonian mountains,
OL,13,     Ga puma battles to raise her
OL,14,     Gbiggest litter yet.
OL,15,G0155FThe Green Planet
